1 setlinecap

mark             
/ISOLatin1Encoding 
  8#000 1 8#054 {StandardEncoding exch get} for 
  /minus 
  8#056 1 8#217 {StandardEncoding exch get} for 
  /dotlessi 
  8#301 1 8#317 {StandardEncoding exch get} for 
  /space /exclamdown /cent /sterling /currency /yen /brokenbar /section 
